OL,5,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FNurse Chloe answers the call when
OL,7,     Fa toddler is brought in with
OL,8,     Fsepsis. Norman, 84, is brought in
OL,9,     Fafter falling out of his mobility
OL,10,     Fscooter.
OL,11,G2100 A&E After Dark
OL,12,     FIn Newham, a boy, 19, lies with a
OL,13,     Fpotentially broken neck after a
OL,14,     Fjudo match - any movement could
OL,15,     Fworsen his injury. Meanwhile,
OL,16,     Fdoctors fight to save a patient
OL,17,     Fwith a collapsed lung.
