OL,5,G2200 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,6,     FA workplace accident ends with a
OL,7,     Fman pushed through a sheet of
OL,8,     Fglass, and responders have to
OL,9,     Fhandle the cuts; a stabbing victim
OL,10,     Frisks bleeding out on the street.
OL,11,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,12,     FDr Toby treats one of the largest
OL,13,     Flipomas the clinic has seen; Dr
OL,14,     FNatalia deals with a supersized
OL,15,     Fwarty lesion; Dr Emma sorts out a
OL,16,     Fcyst that patient Barry's wife has
OL,17,     Fenjoyed squeezing.
