OL,5,G0000 Plastic Surgery Nightmares
OL,6,     FIn this episode, we tell the
OL,7,     Fshocking story of how one woman,
OL,8,     FMarie ended up being rushed into
OL,9,     Fhospital when surgery to remove
OL,10,     Fexcess skin left her with life
OL,11,     Fthreatening sepsis.
OL,12,G0100 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,13,     FA woman suffers with chronic back
OL,14,     Fpain since giving birth to her
OL,15,     Ftwins five years ago. During the
OL,16,     Fprocedure, Hannah was given an
OL,17,     Fepidural that caused nerve damage
OL,18,     Fin her spine.
